{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "biofizic-circumplex",
  "title": "Biofizic Circumplex (arousal REAL x valence PROXY — limitation demo)",
  "tags": ["biofizic", "legacy", "negative-result"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 2,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "READ ME",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Russell circumplex: AROUSAL (Y, valid HR/HRV) x VALENCE (X, unvalidated PPA proxy).** The blue dot is the current state; the ring + emotion labels are a fixed reference. **The horizontal (valence) position is NOT trustworthy** — the proxy is independent noise vs arousal (r~0.07), so the dot drifts left/right largely by chance. Vertical (arousal) position is real. This visualises *why wrist-only cannot place emotion on the valence axis*; the VR decision uses arousal alone."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Circumplex — ring=reference, blue=session points (X=valence proxy, Y=arousal). Quadrants: top=high arousal, right=positive. NW Fear/Anger, NE Happy/Excited, SW Sad/Tired, SE Relaxed/Sleepy.",
      "type": "xychart",
      "gridPos": { "h": 18, "w": 14, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "biofizic-influx" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "biofizic-influx" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "format": "table",
          "queryType": "sql",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT x, y_ring, y_state FROM (SELECT 0.9*sin(g*0.0785398) AS x, 5.5 + 4.5*cos(g*0.0785398) AS y_ring, CAST(NULL AS DOUBLE) AS y_state FROM generate_series(0,80) AS t(g) UNION ALL SELECT v.valence AS x, CAST(NULL AS DOUBLE) AS y_ring, CAST(l.arousal_10 AS DOUBLE) AS y_state FROM biofizic_live l JOIN biofizic_legacy_valence v ON l.time = v.time WHERE l.arousal_10 IS NOT NULL AND $__timeFilter(l.time)) u ORDER BY x"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "seriesMapping": "auto",
        "tooltip": { "mode": "single" },
        "legend": { "showLegend": true, "placement": "bottom" }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "show": "points", "pointSize": { "fixed": 5 }, "axisGridShow": true }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "x" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "min", "value": -1.1 },
              { "id": "max", "value": 1.1 },
              { "id": "custom.axisLabel", "value": "VALENCE proxy (neg <- 0 -> pos) [NOT trustworthy]" }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "y_ring" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "min", "value": 0 },
              { "id": "max", "value": 11 },
              { "id": "custom.axisLabel", "value": "AROUSAL 1-10 (real)" },
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixed": "#cccccc", "mode": "fixed" } },
              { "id": "displayName", "value": "reference ring" }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "y_state" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "fixed": "#3274D9", "mode": "fixed" } },
              { "id": "displayName", "value": "session state" }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Quadrant over time",
      "type": "state-timeline",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 10, "x": 14, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "biofizic-influx" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "biofizic-influx" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "format": "time_series",
          "queryType": "sql",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT l.time, CASE WHEN l.arousal_10 >= 5 AND v.valence >= 0 THEN 3 WHEN l.arousal_10 >= 5 AND v.valence < 0 THEN 4 WHEN l.arousal_10 < 5 AND v.valence >= 0 THEN 1 ELSE 2 END AS quadrant FROM biofizic_live l JOIN biofizic_legacy_valence v ON l.time = v.time WHERE l.arousal_10 IS NOT NULL AND $__timeFilter(l.time) ORDER BY l.time"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            { "type": "value", "options": { "1": { "text": "calm/relaxed", "color": "green", "index": 0 } } },
            { "type": "value", "options": { "2": { "text": "bored/sad", "color": "blue", "index": 1 } } },
            { "type": "value", "options": { "3": { "text": "happy/excited", "color": "yellow", "index": 2 } } },
            { "type": "value", "options": { "4": { "text": "stress/anger", "color": "red", "index": 3 } } }
          ],
          "color": { "mode": "fixed" },
          "min": 1,
          "max": 4
        }
      },
      "options": { "showValue": "never", "mergeValues": true, "rowHeight": 0.9 }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Arousal axis alone (the trustworthy signal)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 10, "x": 14, "y": 13 },
      "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "biofizic-influx" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "influxdb", "uid": "biofizic-influx" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "format": "time_series",
          "queryType": "sql",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT time, arousal_10 FROM biofizic_live WHERE arousal_10 IS NOT NULL AND $__timeFilter(time) ORDER BY time"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "lineWidth": 1, "fillOpacity": 15, "showPoints": "never", "lineInterpolation": "smooth" },
          "min": 1, "max": 10, "decimals": 0
        }
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "showLegend": false }, "tooltip": { "mode": "single" } }
    }
  ]
}
